Name:		kxmleditor
Version:	1.1.3
Release:	1
License:	GPL
Group:		X11/Applications/Editors
Source0:	http://dl.sourceforge.net/%{name}/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
# Source0-md5:	0edae2359e6260524481b920d58580da
